Responsibilities:

  Front line patient services by performing the functions of registration, cashiering, and handling enquiries
  Provide assistance to the Doctor during consultations
  Provide administrative support to the department
  Handling phone calls and inquiries
  Assist in minor procedures
  Process invoice and payment collection
  Booking of referral appointments
  Maintaining inventory levels
  Perform basic triage
  Handle administrative and ad-hoc duties

Requirements:

  Min Education level - diploma (healthcare related)
  Experience, Skills/ certifications healthcare related
  Preferably Entry Level specialized in Healthcare - Nurse/Medical Support &amp; Assistant or equivalent.
